it.polimi.se2019.server.deserialize

Interface RandomDeserializer<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionsDeserializer, ActionUnitDeserializer, AmmoCrateDeserializer, BoardDeserializer, ConditionDeserializer, EffectDeserializer, OptionalEffectDeserializer, PowerUpDeserializer, TileDeserializer, WeaponDeckDeserializer, WeaponDeserializer

    public interface RandomDeserializer<T>
    This is the interface for all of the deserializers, the deserializer has a very tedious job of creating the objects as we need them, This is necessary since gson cannot do this alone. We use a factory specific for each object we want to deserialize.
    Author:
    andreahuang
